name: Flowborne VR - Biofeedback Breathing Meditation
summary: Flowborne VR is a meditative breathwork experience enhanced by biofeedback, tailored to cultivate a peaceful and serene breathing style. Created by psychologists, it seeks to help alleviate stress and promote deep relaxation. Embark on a soothing journey through enchanting worlds, release tension, and master the art of diaphragmatic breathing.
